-- Everton Accepts Manchester City Bid for Midfielder Jack Rodwell
-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 2012-08-12T11:33:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-12/everton-accepts-manchester-city-bid-for-midfielder-jack-rodwell.html
Everton said it accepted an
undisclosed bid from Premier League soccer champion Manchester
City for midfielder  Jack Rodwell .  The 21-year-old is set to have a medical examination at
City today, Everton said in a statement on its website.  Rodwell has made 109 appearances for Everton and played
twice for England.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  